content.rendered:
The Hedge Outdoor Set is a high quality outdoor set, suitable for commercial premises such as Hotels & Bars.

Made with a PVC Rattan and an Aluminium frame, you can be sure that these will stand the test of time. We offer these with a 1 year warranty for your peace of mind.

Made from a brown/beige rattan and comes with cream cushions. The cushions are shower proof, so you can rest easy for those sudden showers and the PVC rattan can be left outside all year round.

The set includes 1 Table & 4 Armchairs or 1 Table & 6 Armchairs

We only sell this product as a set.

Usually available in 3-5 days.

Dimensions in mm:

Armchair(s):
H: 860
W: 670
D: 720
SH: 500

Table:
H: 770
W: 1000
D: 1000

This item requires basic self assembly.
